TY  - JOUR
TI  - An Econometric Analysis of Fertility in Sweden, 1870-1965
AU  - Wilkinson, Maurice
AB  - [The effect of economic constraints upon fertility are analyzed within the theory of household production and allocation of time. The interaction of individual components of family income and the direct economic costs of children are shown to have an increasingly large impact upon Swedish fertility as industrialization proceeds.]
