TY  - JOUR
TI  - Neo-Classical Technology Sets and Properties of Production Possibility Sets
AU  - Otani, Yoshihiko
AB  - [The purpose of this paper is twofold. The first is to obtain a nice characterization of production possibility sets generalizing the well-known nonsubstitution theorem. The second is to obtain a relationship between indispensability of nonproducible commodities and desirable properties of production possibility sets.]
