TY  - JOUR
TI  - Approximations to the Distribution Functions of Theil's k-Class Estimators
AU  - Mariano, Roberto S.
AB  - [For fixed sample size N, the distribution functions of the k-class estimators (k non-stochastic) are approximated up to terms whose order of magnitude is 1/μ, where μ <sup>2</sup> is what is referred to in the literature as the concentration parameter. Similar results are also given for the double k-class estimators.]
